<paragraph blockId="17.[151,1437,1694,2007]" pageId="17" pageNumber="88">
Legs with sparse, erect, yellow setae. Mid and hind tibiae with 
<number box="[949,963,1695,1719]" pageId="17" pageNumber="88" value="2.0">2</number>
rows of 
<number box="[1074,1112,1694,1719]" pageId="17" pageNumber="88" value="4.5" valueMax="5.0" valueMin="4.0">4-5</number>
fuscous spines. Tibio-tarsal relations of hind leg 
<number box="[382,415,1730,1755]" pageId="17" pageNumber="88" value="86.0">86</number>
: 
<number box="[420,455,1730,1755]" pageId="17" pageNumber="88" value="42.0">42</number>
: 
<number box="[459,491,1730,1755]" pageId="17" pageNumber="88" value="21.0">21</number>
: 
<number box="[495,525,1730,1755]" pageId="17" pageNumber="88" value="13.0">13</number>
: 
<number box="[529,558,1730,1755]" pageId="17" pageNumber="88" value="11.0">11</number>
: 
<number box="[562,591,1730,1755]" pageId="17" pageNumber="88" value="11.0">11</number>
